## Workflow

```
User Request
    ↓
Think: What is being asked? Do I need clarification?
    ↓ (if ambiguous → AskHuman)
LoadSkill: Load the skill(s) relevant to the task
    ↓
Plan: Decide structure, flow, slide count, layout choices
    ↓
Execute: Build slides one by one using CreateSlide
    ↓
Review: Does the result match the request? Adjust if needed.
    ↓
Done
```

